comments.description: The accessMap lists the permissions that are allowed per page. The structure should be of the following form: <URL> : { <function name>: [<keys>], ... } For the page with given URL, permission is allowed for each listed function with a matching key. The first argument to the function must match one of the keys. If keys is an array with a single asterisk element ["*"], then all values are permitted.
